<PRE>If your only claim to fame is that you have a supposed above average 
intelligence, then that is really sad. using your intelligence as something 
to brag about is really shallow in itself and if you brag about it offline 
its no wonder that you ar so unpopular. You should try to lighten up and play 
with jokes when their made instead of complaining about it. Hey I believe I 
have an above average intelligence, but then again I have a good social life 
because I have fun messing around with people and cracking jokes, as well as 
doing the unexpected.
